name: Solana Name Service (prev. Bonfida)
public_notice: Bonfida has rebranded to Solana Name Service (SNS). For more information, kindly refer to this announcement and visit the new token page here.

description.en:
SNS is the user identity infrastructure layer on Solana. The .sol domain name can be used as your payment method, web3 username, and on-chain identity.

SNS is building a composable and interactive web3 identity to help anyone anywhere connect to each other with an intuitive and user-friendly omni-chain experience.
